summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the municipal light and power system, providing for the acquisition by condemnation of certain property and property rights in Wenzel Addition and the Southwest 1/4 of the Northeast 1/4 of Section 31, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., for expansion of the "North" Service Center site as a part of certain additions and betterments to the existing system and providing for payment.
